      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and internal test suites confirm correct implementation of linear elastic solid elements and contact formulations used in the pedicle screw model.",
      "rationale": "Each solver in the ensemble was verified against published NAFEMS benchmarks for beam bending, contact pressure, and large-deformation problems representative of the F1717 loading regime. Results agreed within 1% for all benchmark quantities."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
